- I know.

00:03:40.300 --> 00:03:42.666
- But I'm not.
[laughter]

00:03:42.666 --> 00:03:45.766
- Racial profiling
at it's best.

00:03:45.766 --> 00:03:48.400
- All right.
Everybody back--

00:03:48.400 --> 00:03:50.566
