00:05:18.633 --> 00:05:20.633
- Get it, get it, get it,
get it, get it.

00:05:20.633 --> 00:05:22.566
- Come on, Josh.
Come on, Josh.

00:05:22.566 --> 00:05:25.233
This is like a grudge match.
Grudge match.

